9#include <fcntl.h>
10#include <sys/ioctl.h>
11#include "ipf.h"
12
13
14void
15printtqtable(table)
16 ipftq_t *table;
17{
18 int i;
19
20 PRINTF("TCP Entries per state\n");
21 for (i = 0; i < IPF_TCP_NSTATES; i++)
22 PRINTF(" %5d", i);
23 PRINTF("\n");
24
25 for (i = 0; i < IPF_TCP_NSTATES; i++)
26 PRINTF(" %5d", table[i].ifq_ref - 1);
27 PRINTF("\n");
28}
